bibtex mydocument
pdflatex -interaction=batchmode mydocument.tex
```

The resulting PDF document will have an automatically generated table of contents that includes the "Glossary" entry, as well as entries for figures and tables. Note that this example demonstrates adding a glossary to the TOC, but similar techniques can be used to automatically include lists of figures and tables as well.

